{
  "stem": "11723.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, in-- uh, 1952 as a child, it was heartbreaking for me when I had to go and demonstrate and-- and-- and yell, long live Stalin and long live Rakosi, who was the equivalent-- Hungarian equivalent of Stalin.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And inside, I-- I was very, very bitter that these people perhaps killed my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in 1953, fortunately Stalin died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a general amnesty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, uh, let my father go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- I don't know how he got home, because they just dropped him off at the corner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was, uh, practically tortured to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it took him more than a year to recuperate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, uh, then he just went back working with the Jewish congregation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, um, in 1954, I graduated, uh, elementary school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And because I was a capitalist's child, an undesirable element, I could not-- could not have gone to high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the Jewish high school in Budapest where all of us Jewish kids went who were undesirable elements.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it happened to have been a great school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, uh, I had a great time there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have to worry about anti-Semitism or anything of that sort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in, uh-- the next significant event in my life happened in 1956, which is the best thing that ever happened to me-- the Hungarian Revolution.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, I was in-- I just started my third year in, uh, high school in, uh, September.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on October 23, I was on a street car, and, um, we were passing the, uh, offices of the, uh, publisher of the, uh, Hungarian communist newspaper.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw some leaflets flying down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, uh, said to myself, well, that's nothing unusual-- probably some communist propaganda.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
